ReadOnlyAppenderCollection.ToArray returns empty array log4net.Appender.AppenderCollection.ReadOnlyAppenderCollection does not override ToArray().
As a consequence ToArray calls returns always empty arrays.

Fix:
public override IAppender[] ToArray()
{
    return m_collection.ToArray();
}

